                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800"><strong>Ensure Immediate Safety:</strong> Assess the scene for any immediate risks to yourself or others. Your safety and the safety of any students or staff present are paramount.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="list-item">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
