                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800"><strong>Dial 111 Immediately:</strong> Contact emergency services (Police, Fire, and Ambulance). Clearly state the situation and your location.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="list-item">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800"><strong>Preserve the Scene:</strong> As much as possible, avoid disturbing the scene to allow for proper investigation by authorities.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Section II: Secure the Scene, Protect Students & Manage Information -->
        <div class="mb-10">
            <div class="section-header">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 2.1L19 6.3v4.7c0 4.5-3.05 8.68-7 9.9-3.95-1.22-7-5.4-7-9.9V6.3L12 3.1z"/>
                </svg>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">II. Secure the Scene, Protect Students & Manage Information</h2>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="list-item">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
