                    </svg>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800"><strong>Prevent Access & Direct Students:</strong> Secure the area immediately to prevent unauthorised access, especially by students. Direct any students present or nearby to a safe, supervised area away from the scene.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="list-item">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800"><strong>Manage Mobile Phones:</strong> Advise students <strong>not</strong> to use their mobile phones to photograph, record, or share any information. Reassure them official information will be shared by staff.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="list-item">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800"><strong>Await Verification:</strong> Formal verification of death is the responsibility of medical professionals or the police. Do not attempt to verify death yourself.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="list-item">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800"><strong>Note for Police/Coroner:</strong> Be aware that police may prevent the removal of the body to facilitate a thorough investigation.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

