                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800"><strong>Immediate Notification:</strong> As the on-duty staff member, your first and immediate contact is the <strong>House Director</strong>. If the House Director is unavailable, immediately notify the <strong>Director of Boarding</strong> or the <strong>Health Clinic</strong>. The House Director will then immediately inform the Director of Boarding and Health Clinic, initiating the school's crisis protocol. The full crisis team typically includes the Director of Boarding, House Director, Deputy Principal - Pastoral Care, Campus Principal, and Head of School.</p>
                </li>
